divs: Sighting DetailsI was in the backyard letting the dog out and looking at the sky. I noticed the object because of the colors. I wondered what the oject could be. We have viewed this object for about a week with binoculars. It stays in the sky for hours at a time. It has multiple colors that seem to be along its perimeter...I would have to guess star-like or possibly circular...so I am not sure of the shape. I have taken a picture but do not have a floppy drive to see if anything will show up...I couldn't see the object in my viewfinder. I will re-post if the photo shows anything.
Summary: Multicolored object in sky a little south and east of Tinker AFB
